rows.label: qst702804_msg0002
rows.name:
...As expected of the heroes Morumo
recognized. A splendid fight, mo.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0003
rows.name: If you think so, then surrender.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0004
rows.name:
...No, mo! If I don't give up,
my dream will continue, mo!

rows.label: qst702804_msg0005
rows.name: Mo mo mo mo mo mo!

rows.label: qst702804_msg0007
rows.name:
We have to stop him... He'll
get hurt if he falls!

rows.label: qst702804_msg0008
rows.name: That would be his own fault.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0010
rows.name:
Calm down. In any case, he can't
get far on this scaffolding.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0011
rows.name:
We'll just have to
follow him carefully.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0012
rows.name: Follow him? There's no real path.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0013
rows.name: I can leave you behind if you'd prefer.
